===============================================================================
Attribution and homage
===============================================================================

The application is named in homage to Dom André Mocquereau, O.S.B.
(1849–1930), monk of Solesmes, pioneer of neume paleography and founder of
the Paléographie Musicale series. The name and reference are scholarly
acknowledgements and do not imply endorsement by any Solesmes institution.
